name: Tezzy Everydays #3 | Arthur Tezorelli | May 9th, 2021
description: This is the third day of my 1 of 1 pixel art series. Every pixel art piece will involve everyones favorite coin, which most certainly is Tezos. I decided to go with a Happy Days inspired piece for today. Growing up in the 80's, I am a mega Happy Days fan and Fonzi was hands down my fave. He is totally the coolest and I love Henry Winkler as an actor. Tezzy Everydays are created by @clipdad_
